le=\"font-family:楷体\">惊恐障碍</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20960,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 18:00:17","updateTime":"2019-06-22 18:00:17","isTrue":false,"questionId":5343,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">适应障碍</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20961,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 18:00:17","updateTime":"2019-06-22 18:00:17","isTrue":false,"questionId":5343,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">急性应激障碍</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20962,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 18:00:17","updateTime":"2019-06-22 18:00:17","isTrue":true,"questionId":5343,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">创伤后应激障碍</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":1568,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:25:57","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:25:57","name":"精神A2二","questionCnt":20,"tagTypeId":54},{"id":1567,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:24:51","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:24:51","name":"精神A2二","questionCnt":18,"tagTypeId":48}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":5341,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:58:59","topicId":null,"tagId":1567,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":14,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">患者在空旷的操场上散步突然听到两个声音为患者衣着是否暴露而争吵不休，各说各理，而此时周围并无他人，这个症状是</span></span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p style=\"text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">幻听分为评论性幻听、命令性幻听、争论性幻听和思维鸣响。评论性幻听：听到别人在议论自己，议论的内容以负性的批评、讽刺、责骂、诬陷多见。命令性幻听：听到有声音命令自己去做某事，如打人、拒绝进食、自杀或自伤。争论性幻听：听幻觉的内容于患者本人无关，患者听到的是另外两个人的争论，有时舌战的内容可以以患者为中心。思维鸣响：在病人感觉到思维活动的同时，其脑内出现于思维活动一样的言语伴随思维活动而出现。</span></span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":20948,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:58:59","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:58:59","isTrue":false,"questionId":5341,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">思维化声</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20949,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:58:59","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:58:59","isTrue":true,"questionId":5341,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">争论性幻听</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20950,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:58:59","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:58:59","isTrue":false,"questionId":5341,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">评论性幻听</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20951,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:58:59","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:58:59","isTrue":false,"questionId":5341,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">思维鸣响</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20952,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:58:59","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:58:59","isTrue":false,"questionId":5341,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">命令性幻听</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":1568,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:25:57","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:25:57","name":"精神A2二","questionCnt":20,"tagTypeId":54},{"id":1567,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:24:51","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:24:51","name":"精神A2二","questionCnt":18,"tagTypeId":48}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":5339,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:57:45","topicId":null,"tagId":1567,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":13,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">男，</span>35岁，诊断为酒精所致精神障碍。入院后感到身体表面有许多虫子在皮肤上爬行，骚痒难忍，焦躁不安，此症状最可能是</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 楷体;\">酒精性幻觉症</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体;\">:</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体;\">在长期饮酒后，意识清晰状态下出现持续的幻觉，多数患者以听幻觉为主，多为单调的威胁性的声音如枪声、刀砍声或辱骂声。有的患者对幻觉有部分或全部的自知力，这是酒精性幻觉症的特点。幻触：在没有任何刺激时，患者感到皮肤上有某种异常的感觉，如电麻感、虫爬感、针刺感等</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体;\">(A</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体;\">对）。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":20938,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:57:45","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:57:45","isTrue":true,"questionId":5339,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">幻触</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20939,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:57:45","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:57:45","isTrue":false,"questionId":5339,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">本体幻觉</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20940,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:57:45","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:57:45","isTrue":false,"questionId":5339,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">感觉过敏</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20941,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:57:45","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:57:45","isTrue":false,"questionId":5339,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">感觉倒错</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20942,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:57:45","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:57:45","isTrue":false,"questionId":5339,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">错觉</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":1568,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:25:57","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:25:57","name":"精神A2二","questionCnt":20,"tagTypeId":54},{"id":1567,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:24:51","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:24:51","name":"精神A2二","questionCnt":18,"tagTypeId":48}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":5338,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:56:18","topicId":null,"tagId":1567,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":12,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">男，</span>28岁。1个月来3次无明显诱因突发心悸、胸闷、窒息感，浑身冷汗，感觉自己快不行了，极度紧张害怕，持续10余分钟，每次去医院急诊，除心电图是窦性心动过速外，余无异常，事后总担心下次再发作。该患者最可能的诊断是</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">惊恐障碍的诊断要点</span>:(1)以惊恐发作为主要临床特征，发作间歇期基本正常。典型的惊恐发作表现可以分为精神症状和躯体症状。精神症状主要表现为患者突然出现的强烈的惊恐体验，伴濒死感、窒息感或失控感。躯体症状系自主神经功能紊乱所引起，出现心血管系统、呼吸系统和神经系统的症状。(2) 惊恐发作出现在没有客观危险的环境。(3)不局限于已知的或可预测的情境。4) 因难以忍受又无法解脱，而感到痛苦或社会功能受损。(5) 在1 个月内至少有几次 （3次）明显的惊恐发作，或首次发作后继发的焦虑持续 1个月以上。(6) 体格检查无阳性发现。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":20933,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:56:18","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:56:18","isTrue":false,"questionId":5338,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">广泛性焦虑障碍</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20934,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:56:18","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:56:18","isTrue":false,"questionId":5338,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">恐惧性障碍</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20935,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:56:18","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:56:18","isTrue":false,"questionId":5338,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">癔症（分离</span>-转换障碍）</span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20936,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:56:18","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:56:18","isTrue":true,"questionId":5338,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">惊恐障碍</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20937,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:56:18","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:56:18","isTrue":false,"questionId":5338,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">心脏病所致焦虑障碍</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":1568,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:25:57","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:25:57","name":"精神A2二","questionCnt":20,"tagTypeId":54},{"id":1567,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:24:51","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:24:51","name":"精神A2二","questionCnt":18,"tagTypeId":48}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":5336,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:54:46","topicId":null,"tagId":1568,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":11,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">女性，</span>18岁，近1年来认为自己过胖，每日专注于自己的体重、体型，严格限制每日进食量，偶有贪食情况，但饱餐之后，立即自行呕吐，或服泻剂，现出现畏寒体温偏低，月经停止，比标准体重减轻25％，经详细询问病史及各种检查即往无躯体疾病病史，最可能的诊断</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">神经性贪食症此症为周期发作不可控制的多食，可出现于神经性厌食中，但并非必然伴有此症状。此症状群包含两大主要成分，其一是不可抗拒的强迫自己多食，其二是自己设法进行呕吐以避免体重增加，有时则是滥用泻药。此类患者的体重常保持在正常范围之内，女性患者月经仍可正常。女性较为常见。本症以反复发作性暴食和强烈的控制体重的愿望为特征，为防止暴食对体重的影响患者采用各种措施，如呕吐、导泻、增加活动量等，致使体重反低于正常范围。本症多见于年轻女性。结合题干描述考虑选答案</span>A，采用排除法。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":20923,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:54:46","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:54:46","isTrue":true,"questionId":5336,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">神经性厌食症</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20924,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:54:46","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:54:46","isTrue":false,"questionId":5336,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">神经性贪食症</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20925,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:54:46","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:54:46","isTrue":false,"questionId":5336,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">结核症</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20926,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:54:46","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:54:46","isTrue":false,"questionId":5336,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">癌症</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20927,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:54:46","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:54:46","isTrue":false,"questionId":5336,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">甲状腺功能不全</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":1568,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:25:57","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:25:57","name":"精神A2二","questionCnt":20,"tagTypeId":54},{"id":1567,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:24:51","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:24:51","name":"精神A2二","questionCnt":18,"tagTypeId":48}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":5333,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:49:31","topicId":null,"tagId":1567,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":10,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">男，</span>36岁，其妻在一车祸现场丧生，其后患者表现为依赖性强，兴趣变得狭窄，以自我为中心。心理医生认为患者属于应激反应。这类型的应激反应属于</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p style=\"text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">应激的心理反应包括情绪性应激反应、认知性应激反应、行为性应激反应，这三方面的反应不是孤立的，通常是双向调节，构成一个反馈回路系统。认知性应激反应是指应激时唤起注意和认知过程，以适应和应对外界环境变化。但应激较剧烈时，认知能力普遍下降。常见的认知性应激反应表现为：意识障碍，如意识朦胧、意识范围狭小：注意力受损，表现为注意力集中困难、注意范围狭窄等：记忆、思维、想象力减退等。这些负面的认知性应激反应使人陷入灾难中，难以自拔，如偏执个体在应激后出现认知狭窄、偏激、钻牛角尖，平日非常理智的人变得固执、蛮不讲理。也可表现为过分的自我关注，注意自身的感受、想法、信念等内部世界，而非外部世界。情绪性应激反应包括焦虑、抑郁、恐惧、愤怒。行为性应激反应包括积极及消极的行为应对反应。积极的行为性应激可为患者减少压力，甚至可以激发主体的能动性，激励主体克服困难，战胜挫折。而消极的行为性应激则会使个体出现逃避与回避、退化与依赖、敌对与攻击、无助与自怜等行为。</span></span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":20908,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:49:31","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:49:31","isTrue":false,"questionId":5333,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">行为退缩</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20909,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:49:31","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:49:31","isTrue":true,"questionId":5333,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">或战或逃反应</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20910,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:49:31","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:49:31","isTrue":false,"questionId":5333,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">认知反应</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20911,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:49:31","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:49:31","isTrue":false,"questionId":5333,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">情绪反应</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20912,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:49:31","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:49:31","isTrue":false,"questionId":5333,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">自我防御反应</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":1568,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:25:57","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:25:57","name":"精神A2二","questionCnt":20,"tagTypeId":54},{"id":1567,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:24:51","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:24:51","name":"精神A2二","questionCnt":18,"tagTypeId":48}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":5332,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:48:28","topicId":null,"tagId":1568,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":9,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">男性，</span>40岁，1年前提拔到领导岗位，近半年出现脑力活动效率明显下降，体力易疲劳，有时回忆和联想增多且控制不住，兴奋伴有不快感，但无言语运动增多，易激惹，肢体肌肉酸痛，醒后感到不解乏，不愿上班。最可能是患有</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p style=\"text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">神经衰弱：神经衰弱是指由于某些长期存在的精神因素引起脑功能活动过度紧张，从而产生了精神活动能力的减弱。其主要临床特点是易于兴奋又易于疲劳。常伴有各种躯体不适感和睡眠障碍，不少患者病前具有某种易感素质或不良个性。</span></span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":20903,"de