style=\"font-family:楷体\">急性脊髓炎</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20862,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:41:52","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:41:52","isTrue":false,"questionId":5323,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">重症肌无力</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":1568,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:25:57","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:25:57","name":"精神A2二","questionCnt":20,"tagTypeId":54},{"id":1567,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:24:51","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:24:51","name":"精神A2二","questionCnt":18,"tagTypeId":48}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":5319,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:37:29","topicId":null,"tagId":1567,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":4,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">女，</span>30岁。头部受伤后昏迷半小时，清醒后左侧肢体力弱。腰穿血性脑脊液，以后逐渐好转，最可能为</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p style=\"text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">脑挫伤是受伤局部脑皮质形状保留而实质出血和（或）肿胀的一种闭合性脑损伤。当头部遭受钝器打击或交通事故、高坠，头部与其他物体碰撞时，头部作直线加速、直线减速或旋转运动，此时脑组织与颅骨的运动速度不一致；或与粗糙不平的颅骨内板碰撞；或在高低凹凸的颅底骨板上滑动；或因脑各部的运动速度不一致而产生剪切力；或受骨折区的直接损伤或脑疝的挤压，脑实质都可能发生挫（裂）伤。腰椎穿刺：有助于了解脑脊液中含血情况，可赖以与脑震荡鉴别，同时，能够测定颅内压及引流血性脑脊液。</span></span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":20839,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:37:29","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:37:29","isTrue":false,"questionId":5319,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">脑震荡</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20840,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:37:29","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:37:29","isTrue":true,"questionId":5319,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">脑挫伤</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20841,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:37:29","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:37:29","isTrue":false,"questionId":5319,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">急性硬膜外血肿</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20842,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:37:29","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:37:29","isTrue":false,"questionId":5319,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">急性硬膜下血肿</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20843,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:37:29","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:37:29","isTrue":false,"questionId":5319,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">脑内血肿</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":1568,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:25:57","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:25:57","name":"精神A2二","questionCnt":20,"tagTypeId":54},{"id":1567,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:24:51","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:24:51","name":"精神A2二","questionCnt":18,"tagTypeId":48}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":5318,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:36:21","topicId":null,"tagId":1568,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":3,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\">30岁男性，劳动中突感剧烈头痛、呕吐，一度意识不清，醒后颈枕部痛，右侧眼睑下垂，右瞳孔大、颈强，克氏征阳性。最可能的诊断是&nbsp;</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">本题问的是</span>“最可能的诊断”，因为患者年轻、而且“在劳动中”发病，故蛛网膜下腔出血的可能性大。而脑出血多见于老年人、高血压患者。因此，最佳答案是E。小脑出血：多数表现突然起病的眩晕、频繁呕吐，枕部头痛，一侧上下肢共济失调而无明显瘫痪，可有眼球震颤，无脑膜刺激征。脑干出血：可立刻昏迷、四肢瘫、针尖样瞳孔，数小时内死亡，无脑膜刺激征。脑出血、脑疝：多数有高血压病史，中老年人多见,寒冷季节发病较多。大多在活动时起病，突发剧烈头痛伴呕吐,多有意识障碍,发病时血压较高，神经系统局灶症候与出血的部位和出血量有关。脑疝有多种类型主要表现意识障碍，颅内压增高症状，瞳孔改变，但脑出血及脑疝一般均无脑膜刺激征。蛛网膜下腔出血：（1）头痛、呕吐，突发剧烈头痛、呕吐、颜面苍白、全身冷汗。如头痛局限某处有定位意义，如前头痛提示小脑幕上和大脑半球（单侧痛）、后头痛表示后颅凹病变。（2）意识和精神症状，多数患者无意识障碍，但可有烦躁不安。危重者可有谵妄，不同程度的意识不清及至昏迷，少数可出现癫痫发作和精神症状。（3）脑膜刺激征，青壮年病人多见且明显，伴有颈背部痛。老年患者、出血早期或深昏迷者可无脑膜刺激征。（4）其他表现，如低热、腰背腿痛等。亦可见轻偏瘫，视力障碍，第Ⅲ、Ⅴ、Ⅵ、Ⅶ等颅神经麻痹，视网膜片状出血和视乳头水肿等。此外还可并发上消化道出血和呼吸道感染等。此题主要鉴别要点：脑膜刺激征。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":20834,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:36:21","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:36:21","isTrue":false,"questionId":5318,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">急性脑膜炎</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20835,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:36:21","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:36:21","isTrue":false,"questionId":5318,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">脑出血、脑疝</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20836,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:36:21","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:36:21","isTrue":false,"questionId":5318,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">小脑出血</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20837,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:36:21","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:36:21","isTrue":false,"questionId":5318,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">脑干出血</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20838,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:36:21","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:36:21","isTrue":true,"questionId":5318,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">蛛网膜下腔出血</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":1568,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:25:57","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:25:57","name":"精神A2二","questionCnt":20,"tagTypeId":54},{"id":1567,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:24:51","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:24:51","name":"精神A2二","questionCnt":18,"tagTypeId":48}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":5316,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:34:26","topicId":null,"tagId":1567,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":2,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 楷体;\">女，</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体;\">22岁，医学生，最近与男友发生了激烈的争执，以致两人分手，情绪极度低落，也十分愤恨，来找学校心理咨询师寻求帮助，心理咨询师针对其情绪的调节提出的办法中不适合的是</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">对于情绪调节可采用：改变认知、心</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">理</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">应对、降低期望、放松训练等</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">；</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">不断宣泄不是调节情绪的方法，故本题选</span>A。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":20824,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:34:26","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:34:26","isTrue":true,"questionId":5316,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">不断宣泄</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20825,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:34:26","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:34:26","isTrue":false,"questionId":5316,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">改变认知</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20826,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:34:26","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:34:26","isTrue":false,"questionId":5316,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">放松训练</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20827,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:34:26","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:34:26","isTrue":false,"questionId":5316,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">心</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">理</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">应对</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":20828,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-22 17:34:26","updateTime":"2019-06-22 17:34:26","isTrue":false,"questionId":5316,"content":"<p><span s